content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 8 ยง 113.14 - Effect of saturday, sundays and holidays

State Regulations

If the last day for service or filing of an appeal paper, order or any other paper under the provisions of this Chapter falls on a

Saturday, Sunday or legal holiday, filing or service may be made on the next
business day. Notes
